  "title": "Product Engineer",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Descriptions:</u></p><p>1) Embedded hardware/firmware development of wired & wireless product and integration.</p><p>2) Technologies related to ARM/PIC/RTOS, Ethernet, Zigbee, C/C++ etc...</p><p>3) Involves in Product management.</p><p>4) Involves in complete development cycle from concept to commercialization.</p><p>5) Good understanding of general sensors and controllers, in both hardware and software applications.</p><p>6) Exposure in smart building system, e.g. air-con system, lighting control, electrical panel, BMS etc.</p><p><br /><u>Job Requirements:</u></p><p>1) Degree in Embedded System/Electronics/Computer/Telecommunication Engineering.</p><p>2) Passion in Engineering.</p><p>3) Good understanding of embedded analog/digital circuit, electrical/mechanical, RF protocol.</p><p>4) Hardworking, analytical and systematic.</p><p><br />Interested applicant, pls send CV with expected salary to: jobs@tcam.com.sg</p>",
