    "uen": "200103565N",
    "description": "<p>   TCAM TECHNOLOGY PTE. LTD.</p>  <div>   TCAM Technology Pte Ltd (Singapore) is a “State of the Art” technologies company, incorporated in 2001. Our core competencies are in wireless telemetry products related to SMS/GSM/GPRS/3G, for applications in M2M (Machine to Machine) , IoT (Internet of Things), AMR (Automatic Meter Reading) and SCADA (Supervisory Control And Data Acquisition). We have a team of highly qualified business development and R&D professionals. For the past ten over years, we have developed many products and technology platforms for our valued partners. Our TMAS brand name, technologies, products, system solutions etc are landed in many countries from Asia, Europe, Africa, Middle East and Australia.</div>  <div>   <p>    We are the founding member of IoT Asia (Internet of Things, http://www.internetofthingsasia.com/). We continue to invest heavily in R&D, focusing in M2M and IoT technologies, creating new values for our partners. A consistent dedication to the development of continual improvement of technologies in ways that entails with the needs of customers, is and always the source of our strength. Guided by this vision, we have always striven to ensure that our technological diversification is quickly reflected in solutions that allow customers to add value to their own products. In addition, we are able to advice and provide total integrated solution to solve customer’s problem, improve in their work flow effectively and efficiently.</p>   <p>    TCAM’s success has been due in large part to its corporate philosophy that has emphasized focusing into its core business to satisfy the customer’s requirement for high quality telemetry solutions.</p>  </div>  ",
